title.rendered: Stratus & Unite Folding Outdoor Bistro Dining Set – round or square

content.rendered:
The Stratus & Unite Folding Outdoor Bistro Dining Set comprises: two or four of our stackable ultra strong Stratus chairs plus our ultra strong Unite folding Dining Table with a Werzalit Laminate top for great integrity. 

The Stratus Chair is stackable 8 high and is made with one-mould polypropylene. The Unite folding Table Base is made from nano-coated aluminium, suitable for indoor and outdoor use. 

Ideal for commercial use, such as coffee shops, hotels and care homes. Easy to clean and care for – suitable for all weather, indoor and out!

5 year warranty.

Dimensions in mm:

– Stratus Side Chair: 460D x 500W x 810H x 455 Seat Height

– Unite Folding Dining Base: 720H

– Werzalit Top: overall 27mm thick

This item requires basic self assembly.
